## Description

Report and tax calculator for transaction on Luna blockchain

## Configuration

```bash
$ cp ./.env.example .env
```
Set the port and database configuration in the .env file

## Installation

```bash
$ npm install

$ cd ./parser

$ npm install
```

## Running the app

```bash
# development
$ npm run dev

# production
$ npm run prod

```
